      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      * PROGRAM NAME
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. ARR00064.
      ******************************************************************
      *                 INTERFACE SISTEMAS EXTERNO                     *
      ******************************************************************
      * OBJECTIVO: Obtençăo dados do utilizador                        *
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                      PIC  X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE DO ARR00064   '.
      ******************************************************************
      * PROGRAM CONTROL (PGM)
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-PRG-CTL.
           05 WS-PRG-NAM               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARR00064'.
      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS DE TRABALHO (VARTRAB)
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARTRAB.
           05 WN-INDICE                PIC  9(03).
           05 WS-CBAL-TXT              PIC  X(04).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-CBAL-TXT.
             10 WS-CBAL                PIC  9(04).
      ******************************************************************
      * SWITCHES  (SWI)
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-SWITCH.
           05 WN-SWF                   PIC  9(01) VALUE 0.
              88 WC-SWF-INI                       VALUE 0.
              88 WC-SWF-FIM                       VALUE 8.
              88 WC-SWF-ERR                       VALUE 9.
              88 WC-SWF-TER                       VALUE 8 THRU 9.
      ******************************************************************
      * TABELAS
      ******************************************************************
      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  WC-CONSTAN.
           05 CON-ACTIVO               PIC  X(01) VALUE 'A'.
      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
      *--- constantes de erro
           COPY ETCK0001.
      *--- constantes do modulo
           COPY ETCK0002.
      *---
       77  WA-CODERRO                    PIC  X(07) VALUE SPACES.
      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-IND                   PIC S9(04) COMP-3.
      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0100 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ONLINE         '.

      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *--- Area de processamento de erros
           COPY ETCL0002.
      *--- Area de chamada ŕ Rotina ARR00064
           COPY ETCL0064.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                ETCL0064-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *-
           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *-
           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *-
       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.
      ******************************************************************
      * 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-DB2-LOG.
           INITIALIZE ETCL0002-AREA-ERRO.
           SET ETCL0002-RCODE-OK            TO TRUE
           SET WC-SWF-INI                   TO TRUE

           PERFORM 1100-PROC-INICIAL
              THRU 1100-PROC-INICIAL-EXIT.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      * 1100-PROC-INICIAL                                             **
      ******************************************************************
       1100-PROC-INICIAL.

           IF NOT ETCL0002-VERSAO-VIA
              SET  ETCL0002-RCODE-VAL       TO TRUE
              MOVE ETCK0002-APL-ET          TO ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
              MOVE WS-PRG-NAM               TO ETCL0002-CPROGRAM
              MOVE 'VERSAO ERRADA'          TO ETCL0002-GINFO-ERRO
              SET  ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO TRUE
              MOVE ETCK0001-VERSAO-BANKA    TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
           END-IF.

       1100-PROC-INICIAL-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      * 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE ETCL0064-USER              TO ARCD0100-GUSERNAME.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT CNOME
                   , CPERFIL
                   , ISTATUS
                   , CCENTRO
                INTO :ARCD0100-CNOME
                   , :ARCD0100-CPERFIL
                   , :ARCD0100-ISTATUS
                   , :ARCD0100-CCENTRO
                FROM ARVT0100_UTILIZADOR
               WHERE GUSERNAME = :ARCD0100-GUSERNAME
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE SQLCA                      TO ETCL0002-SQLCA   .

           IF ETCL0002-SQL-OK
              MOVE ARCD0100-CNOME          TO ETCL0064-NOME
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-CFUNCAO        TO ETCL0064-
              MOVE ARCD0100-CPERFIL        TO ETCL0064-GRPR
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-CLINGUA        TO ETCL0064-
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-GPASSWORD      TO ETCL0064-
              MOVE ARCD0100-ISTATUS        TO ETCL0064-SITU
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-CEMPRESA       TO ETCL0064-

              MOVE ARCD0100-CCENTRO        TO WS-CBAL-TXT
              IF WS-CBAL NOT NUMERIC
                MOVE ZEROES TO WS-CBAL
              END-IF

              MOVE WS-CBAL                 TO ETCL0064-BAL

      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-CCENTRO        TO ETCL0064-BAL
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-CMOED          TO ETCL0064-
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-MCUSTMED       TO ETCL0064-
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-DDATINI        TO ETCL0064-
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-DDATFIM        TO ETCL0064-
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-CUSERID        TO ETCL0064-
      **R     MOVE ARCD0100-HTIMEEST       TO ETCL0064-
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-NSEG
              MOVE SPACES                  TO ETCL0064-ECMD
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-NIVC
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-NFUN
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-QAUT
              MOVE SPACES                  TO ETCL0064-GERC
              MOVE SPACES                  TO ETCL0064-TUTL
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-CDGA
              MOVE SPACES                  TO ETCL0064-USCR
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-DTCR
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-HOCR
              MOVE SPACES                  TO ETCL0064-USDE
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-DTDE
              MOVE ZEROES                  TO ETCL0064-HODE
           ELSE
              SET  ETCL0002-RCODE-VAL      TO TRUE
              MOVE ETCK0002-APL-ET         TO ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
              MOVE WS-PRG-NAM              TO ETCL0002-CPROGRAM
              MOVE ETCK0001-SELECT-PPAEMP  TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
              SET  ETCL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO TRUE
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
      * 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.

           CONTINUE.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
            EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                       AREA DE PROCEDURES                       *
      ******************************************************************
